Name: Fantasy Jigsaw Puzzle 4
About the game: Challenging 6 x 6 jigsaw puzzles, featuring epic fantasy female characters. Relaxing background music to match the fantasy theme and mood. Features: 12 different puzzles to solve Timer, to see how long it takes to solve a puzzle Gallery where you can view all the puzzle images you have solved. Be among the fastest puzzle solvers to achieve a top spot in our Leaderboards and unlock various achievements.
